:name:
Fera III

:coretxt:
You are able to turn into several animals. Your total mass does not change.
Each of those still count as part of the body so losing those will result in parts of the body missing.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
Has befriended an feral animal or \SecretNameFeraB{}.

